{
  "stem": "964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I worked in a bakery-- fine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have bread already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My younger brother wanted to go further in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because somehow, he found out-- I don't know how, so many years passed by already-- that he wanted to go to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to be a [NON-ENGLISH] in the town.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was left all by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my-- the one brother before the oldest, he-- somehow, he settled in a [NON-ENGLISH], you know, [NON-ENGLISH] where Jewish people-- not a shul, but there's people come and pray.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they settled there in the [NON-ENGLISH], and slept on the floor with a little straw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they slept there on the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was working-- working-- I got work in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was young, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I got to work in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I work in the bakery, so fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got bread already and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But after a while, all these people had to leave the town because the [NON-ENGLISH] ordered up all the refugees, people that are not natives, they have to leave.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had to be 100 kilometers away from the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I took a passport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You had to take a passport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or you take a passport or they send you back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I figured as long-- I'm a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even if I have a Russian passport, if Poland's going to be again Poland, if Poland's going to be liberated, I probably always will be able to go back to Poland because I was born there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took that passport and-- and I went away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out that one uncle of mine is in Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is-- this is not far from Lvov, if you know the town, Lvov.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not far from Lvov.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
